:: Public Holidays
: New Year's Day
"Новий Рік"                                                         public on january 1
: New Year's Day Substitute Holiday
"Новий Рік"                                                         public on ( (([january 1] == [saturday after ([january 1])]) || ([january 1] == [sunday after ([january 1])])) ? [monday after ([january 1])] : noop )

